993
00:42:01,519 --> 00:42:03,979
so we've set up
this little fire inside for you.

994
00:42:04,063 --> 00:42:05,689
Wow, this is really well made.

995
00:42:05,773 --> 00:42:06,774
Super cute.

996
00:42:06,857 --> 00:42:09,068
Seeing as this is our last night,

997
00:42:09,151 --> 00:42:11,195
I hope it becomes
a memorable time in your life

998
00:42:11,278 --> 00:42:13,614
