Chae-won, please come up here.

1003
00:42:28,170 --> 00:42:31,507
On the count of three,
please press this button.

1004
00:42:31,590 --> 00:42:33,175
Come this way.

1005
00:42:33,259 --> 00:42:35,302
- What's gonna happen?
- Press it when I tell you to.

1006
00:42:35,386 --> 00:42:37,221
