1040
00:44:29,875 --> 00:44:31,585
Hey, Hye-jeong! Come on!

1041
00:44:36,006 --> 00:44:39,093
PUMP UP THE MOOD

1042
00:44:39,176 --> 00:44:41,220
Hey, come on! Dance! Let's see it!

1043
00:44:43,222 --> 00:44:45,432
THAT'S MY FRIEND

1044
00:44:45,516 --> 00:44:46,558
Hey, come on!

1045
00:44:47,267 --> 00:44:48,977
HERE COMES GWIYEOWON

1046
00:44:49,061 --> 00:44:50,562
Gwiyeowon!

1047
00:44:52,189 --> 00:44:53,357
Great, great!

1048
00:44:53,440 --> 00:44:55,317
GREAT, I LOVE IT

1049
00:44:55,401 --> 00:44:56,694
Yeah, that's great!

1050
00:44:57,319 --> 00:44:59,279
All right.

1051
00:44:59,363 --> 00:45:01,115
