Go, Kwang-chul!

1055
00:45:06,870 --> 00:45:07,996
TO THE LEFT

1056
00:45:08,080 --> 00:45:10,165
DOWN

1057
00:45:10,249 --> 00:45:11,709
BACKWARDS

1058
00:45:11,792 --> 00:45:14,294
Wow, he's good! He's good!

1059
00:45:14,378 --> 00:45:16,463
Everyone, jump! Put your hands up!

1060
00:45:16,547 --> 00:45:17,589
Wow!

1061
00:45:17,673 --> 00:45:19,425
