It's your turn. Get in there!

1064
00:45:29,017 --> 00:45:31,729
WIGGLE, WIGGLE

1065
00:45:32,271 --> 00:45:34,273
AAAAAAAAAH, I LOVE IT

1066
00:45:34,356 --> 00:45:35,691
I love it!

1067
00:45:35,774 --> 00:45:38,235
A NEW FANGIRL IS BORN

1068
00:45:38,318 --> 00:45:40,320
PLUS A DIE-HARD FAN

1069
00:45:43,699 --> 00:45:45,200
I love it!

1070
