- Huh?

1082
00:46:19,401 --> 00:46:21,320
- Getting ready for something?
- Not yet.

1083
00:46:21,403 --> 00:46:23,238
It's talent show time.

1084
00:46:23,906 --> 00:46:26,909
So I feel like I should probably have
this person go first.

1085
00:46:26,992 --> 00:46:28,786
All right, Dad! Come on up.

1086
00:46:30,287 --> 00:46:32,664
Let's go Kwang-chul!

1087
00:46:33,457 --> 00:46:34,875
- All right.
- Let's go.

1088
00:46:34,958 --> 00:46:37,085
- The kids are getting up.
- The whole family's doing it?

1089
00:46:37,169 --> 00:46:38,378
Wow, that's so cool!

1090
00:46:38,462 --> 00:46:40,130
I didn't think we'd go first.

1091
00:46:40,214 --> 00:46:42,966
Come up and show us what you got.

1092
00:46:43,675 --> 00:46:44,676
Get ready.

1093
00:46:44,760 --> 00:46:46,386
Whoa, what's that?

1094
00:46:46,470 --> 00:46:48,430
"Hyo-ri, Hyo-ri, we love thee"?

1095
00:46:48,514 --> 00:46:50,349
Maybe they're dancing to
a Lee Hyo-ri song.

1096
00:46:50,432 --> 00:46:52,059
- Oh right, good thinking.
- I think so.

1097
00:46:52,142 --> 00:46:53,685
Hello, everyone. I'm Park Kwang-chul.

1098
00:46:53,769 --> 00:46:55,646
I'm Chae-eun and Chae-won's dad

1099
00:46:55,729 --> 00:46:58,315
