"young-at-heart in their 40s."

1100
00:46:59,233 --> 00:47:00,609
Looking great!

1101
00:47:00,692 --> 00:47:03,403
Truth is,
I thought Hyo-ri was going to be here.

1102
00:47:03,487 --> 00:47:05,531
It would've been nice for her to see this.

1103
00:47:05,614 --> 00:47:07,825
- She helped us rehearse earlier.
- Oh, really?

1104
00:47:07,908 --> 00:47:08,909
Yes.

1105
00:47:08,992 --> 00:47:12,037
That was great. Your expressions
are great too. Just be confident.

1106
00:47:12,120 --> 00:47:15,499
Like this. It's all about the vibe.
The vibe, you know?

1107
00:47:15,582 --> 00:47:19,044
Yeah, and for this walk,
it's not "one, two."

1108
00:47:19,127 --> 00:47:21,004
It's "one, two. Shimmy as you go.

1109
00:47:21,088 --> 00:47:23,966
One, two, three, yes, four,

1110
00:47:24,049 --> 00:47:26,885
five, six, seven, eight."

1111
00:47:26,969 --> 00:47:29,179
To the side. So you're showing your line.

1112
00:47:29,263 --> 00:47:31,807
- <i>Baby, baby, baby, baby girl</i>
- That's so good.

1113
00:47:31,890 --> 00:47:33,350
- As expected.
- You get it, right?

1114
00:47:34,351 --> 00:47:36,979
PRACTICING THE DANCE TOGETHER

1115
00:47:37,688 --> 00:47:40,732
That's it! It's way better than before.
You get it, right?

1116
00:47:40,816 --> 00:47:43,485
You have to get a good
grip when you go to rip it.

1117
00:47:43,569 --> 00:47:46,154
Let's give our first act
a big round of applause!

1118
00:47:48,866 --> 00:47:50,742
Music, please.

1119
00:47:50,826 --> 00:47:53,912
Wait, "Hey Girl"? No way.

1120
00:47:53,996 --> 00:47:55,163
Music please!

1121
00:47:55,247 --> 00:47:58,083
"U-GO-GIRL" (FEAT. NASSUN)
BY LEE HYO-RI

1122
00:48:01,420 --> 00:48:03,380
- Confidence.
- They look so pretty.

1123
00:48:03,463 --> 00:48:04,590
Yeah, they do.

1124
00:48:06,258 --> 00:48:07,926
RIPPED KWANG-CHUL

1125
00:48:15,392 --> 00:48:17,185
Wow! His body's insane!

1126
00:48:17,269 --> 00:48:18,353
IN THE WAY

1127
00:48:19,229 --> 00:48:21,106
A DRAMATIC SHIRT SLAM

1128
00:48:26,528 --> 00:48:28,238
So pretty!

1129
00:48:31,116 --> 00:48:32,451
AM I PRETTY?

1130
00:48:32,534 --> 00:48:33,535
Girl!

1131
00:48:34,828 --> 00:48:36,538
Wow, so cute!

1132
00:48:38,874 --> 00:48:40,417
They're good!

1133
00:48:41,835 --> 00:48:43,295
Ho!

1134
00:48:44,588 --> 00:48:45,964
Hey, you go, girl!

1135
00:48:46,048 --> 00:48:49,092
<i>De-re, de-re, dat, dat, dat girl! </i>

1136
00:48:51,053 --> 00:48:52,179
JUST AS HYO-RI TAUGHT HER

1137
00:48:52,262 --> 00:48:53,347
Go Kwang-chul!

1138
00:48:56,475 --> 00:48:58,393
POLICE SPECIAL OPERATIONS OFFICER
ON A DOPAMINE HIGH

1139
00:48:59,978 --> 00:49:01,188
Wow, he's really good.

1140
00:49:05,692 --> 00:49:07,527
Let's give it up for them!

1141
00:49:07,611 --> 00:49:10,530
- Wow, that was amazing.
- Wow! Give them a big hand.

1142
00:49:10,614 --> 00:49:12,783
- What a great first performance.
- Yeah, amazing.

1143
00:49:12,866 --> 00:49:14,910
How is he in such good shape?

1144
00:49:14,993 --> 00:49:17,287
Wow, seriously. Amazing.

1145
00:49:17,371 --> 00:49:19,831
Seriously. That was awesome.

1146
00:49:19,915 --> 00:49:22,000
- Totally awesome.
- You guys were amazing.

1147
00:49:22,084 --> 00:49:24,920
Did you see? They just ripped
their dad's shirt right off.

1148
00:49:25,003 --> 00:49:26,672
NEVER SEEN A DAD'S SHIRT
GET RIPPED BEFORE

1149
00:49:26,755 --> 00:49:28,882
I mean, if my dad told me to do that,
I couldn't.

1150
00:49:28,966 --> 00:49:31,259
- That was so cool. Yeah.
- It was just incredible.

1151
00:49:31,343 --> 00:49:34,554
When we were practicing,
my dad started to get really hot

1152
00:49:34,638 --> 00:49:35,889
