1156
00:49:41,144 --> 00:49:43,480
We're gonna need something
that's really going to pop."

1157
00:49:43,563 --> 00:49:47,693
So Chae-won and I decided that
we should start by ripping his shirt off.

1158
00:49:47,776 --> 00:49:50,612
We ripped the shirt and tore up the stage.

1159
00:49:50,696 --> 00:49:52,698
