He nailed that roundhouse kick.

1183
00:51:15,614 --> 00:51:17,657
I guess we shouldn't mess with Bryan.

1184
00:51:17,741 --> 00:51:20,577
- And did you guys see that smile?
- Yeah.

1185
00:51:20,660 --> 00:51:22,829
Our two staff members,
please come up here.

1186
00:51:22,913 --> 00:51:25,665
Our tall guys. They're over six feet tall.

1187
00:51:25,749 --> 00:51:27,667
Wait, how many is that?

1188
00:51:27,751 --> 00:51:29,961
- There's five boards.
- Isn't that too many?

1189
00:51:30,045 --> 00:51:32,422
- No, it's fine. Yeah.
- It's okay? All right.

1190
00:51:32,506 --> 00:51:34,132
Here we go.

1191
00:51:34,216 --> 00:51:36,301
Oh, my gosh! Oh, my gosh!

1192
00:51:37,344 --> 00:51:39,638
EYES OPEN WIDE

1193
00:51:39,721 --> 00:51:41,139
Let's hear it!

1194
00:51:42,933 --> 00:51:44,434
One more! Help him, Kwang-soo.

1195
00:51:44,976 --> 00:51:46,478
SCARED

1196
00:51:46,561 --> 00:51:47,896
Oh, don't worry.

1197
00:51:47,979 --> 00:51:49,689
