- Yeah, it'll be fine.

1198
00:51:58,740 --> 00:52:00,158
JAW-DROPPING

1199
00:52:00,242 --> 00:52:02,244
That's so satisfying.

1200
00:52:02,327 --> 00:52:05,247
Big hand for Bryan!

1201
00:52:07,082 --> 00:52:08,583
Wow!

1202
00:52:08,667 --> 00:52:12,337
That was Bryan with an awesome
taekwondo demonstration.

1203
00:52:12,420 --> 00:52:15,882
Now, let's invite our next performer,
Yeo-won.

1204
00:52:15,966 --> 00:52:18,718
Come on up and show us what you got!

1205
00:52:18,802 --> 00:52:20,428
Gwiyeowon!

1206
00:52:20,512 --> 00:52:22,139
I can't wait for this.

1207
00:52:22,222 --> 00:52:24,349
What did you prepare for us, Yeo-won?

1208
00:52:24,432 --> 00:52:27,060
Well, I prepared a little dance
to perform for you all.

1209
00:52:27,144 --> 00:52:29,062
- Okay.
- I will say it's kind of silly.

1210
00:52:29,146 --> 00:52:30,230
Oh, great, great.

1211
00:52:30,313 --> 00:52:34,276
All right, everyone. This is Gwiyeowon.
Yeah, let's give it up for her!

1212
00:52:37,612 --> 00:52:39,656
