- Here we go.
- <i>Real, real, real, real </i>

1216
00:52:58,842 --> 00:53:00,343
What is that?

1217
00:53:00,427 --> 00:53:01,970
"PITIFUL" BY YOUNGTAK

1218
00:53:03,138 --> 00:53:04,598
Gwiyeowon! Gwiyeowon!

1219
00:53:04,681 --> 00:53:07,559
<i>Real, real, real, real, it's real </i>

1220
00:53:07,642 --> 00:53:09,269
